": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerda_Steyn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerda_Steyn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa's road running darlingGerda Steynfinished\\u00a0a somewhat surprising45thin the women's marathon at theParis Olympics 2024on Sunday.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 412, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999849933, \"rank\": 1.511251452585977e-11, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy the Paris Olympic Games 2024 experience at your favourite ATKV Resort!\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ATKV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Steyn crossed the line in a time of2:32:51, well outside her South African record over the distance.\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From early on in the race, those following closely on television would have noticed that the 34-year-old was conspicuous by her absence among the lead runners.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 892, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Post-race, Gerda Steyntook to social mediato explain that she did not have her best day out on the roads of the French capital.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8659230565373167, \"rank\": 0.15256642445257662, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Wow, what an experience!!!\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(but I am really glad it's over) \\ud83e\\udd23The crowds were unbelievable and I will never forget this experience everrrr!!\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you to those who have literally showered me with support and even though I did not run in the way I feel I am capable of, or trained for, I am still really proud to be part of this and I hope that my results today will also be a reminder to always keep going, even when the going gets tough \\ud83d\\udcaa\\ud83c\\udffe\\ud83d\\udcaa\\ud83c\\udffeI did not feel good from the start and knew early on that it would be a tough day out, but I never thought about giving up because of all of YOU \\ud83e\\udef5\\ud83c\\udffd who always cheer me on and believe in me, no matter what challenge I take on!I am living my dream life and today's results will not change any of that!!\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"!\\ud83d\\udc9a\\ud83d\\udc9b\\ud83d\\udc9a\\ud83d\\udc9b\\ud83d\\udc9a\\ud83d\\udc9bCongratulations to@cianoldknowand@irvette_van_zyl- we DID IT!!!!\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1836, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"!#greentrio\\ud83c\\uddff\\ud83c\\udde6Now onto the Closing ceremony and some downtime with all my loved ones \\ud83e\\udd73\\ud83e\\udd73Yehaaah!!\\\"\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1839, \"end\": 1842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dissociative_identity_disorder\", \"score\": 0.9999999999363354, \"rank\": 6.341325577355442e-11, \"text\": \"DID\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dissociative_identity_disorder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dissociative_identity_disorder\"}, {\"begin\": 1843, \"end\": 1845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Information_technology\", \"score\": 0.999998075196833, \"rank\": 1.3584324628039177e-06, \"text\": \"IT\", \"